Class ElementLoad

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.model.NamedObject
      • fem.components.ElementLoad
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IElementLoad, java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable, INamedObject, IStreamable

    public class ElementLoad
extends NamedObject
implements IElementLoad
    This class is abstract with super class IElementload. Class contains generic get and set methods required for implementing a element load into a finite element.
    Author:
    Darren Sulon
